# BC-3.1.5 How to accelerate your innovation mindset? 

## About this chapter? 
This paragraph is about accelerating yourself and getting you and your team/organization in an innovation mindset. Innovation management is a learned capability. In other words, skills can be acquired and applied to the successful execution of the process. 
 

